title: #FBF - How to Live Your Calling Now
description:
Listen in as Emily and Kathleen chat with Tara Mohr, author of Playing Big. They share practical ways to step into your calling immediately, how to recognize your inner critic, and ways to use your inner critic to your benefit.. If you want to hear more of this conversation, check out Episode 55 - Playing Big With Tara Mohr >>
